label: 金
対訳語: The dynasty of the Golden Tartars, or the Nü-chên, better known as the Ju-chên.
本: Early Japanese History c. 40 B.C.-A.D. 1167,  Part B . Princeton University Press . 1937
説明文: In North China from 1115 to 1234. They overthrew the Liao dynasty of the Ch'I-tan, but were overthrown in turn by the Mongols.
